Class Parallelepiped

  • java.lang.Object
    • assignment5.Shape
      • assignment5.Parallelepiped
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.lang.Comparable

    public class Parallelepiped
extends Shape
    Parallelepiped class extends Shape.java which has a Point3D variable that correspond to the center point in a 3 dimensional shape. It also has accessor methods for returning the distance from origin (0,0,0) to the center, the surface area and the volume. The getVolume() and getSurfaceArea() methods are overridden to return the volume and surface area of a Parallelepiped.
